Quickstrike:





Quickstrike groaned and sighed at the same time. He studied 
Stingtra's damaged body. "All right," he said. "Bring 'er in. But 
put 'er optics off-line when ya put 'er in th' CR chamber." He 
stepped to the side, to let Vemonous by.
